cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to an unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security setup phase and prevent successful connection establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the hardware log level to an invalid enum value will cause logging configuration errors and disrupt system monitoring capabilities.
du.explanation_zh: 將硬體日誌級別設定為無效的枚舉值會導致日誌配置錯誤，並干擾系統監控功能。
